description: Sends a request to enable data ingest for a member account that has a status of ACCEPTED_BUT_DISABLED. For valid member accounts, the status is updated as follows.

parameters.name: GraphArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the behavior graph.

parameters.name: AccountId
parameters.description: The account ID of the member account to try to enable. The account must be an invited member account with a status of ACCEPTED_BUT_DISABLED.
